Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_shadow=0 then SHADOW OFF if gs_shadow=1 then SHADOW ON
!!! 3D Feedback to editing IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE ENDIF
IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF THEN END
PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL gs_resol
!!! ************************************************************* !!! *** 3D HOTSPOTs *********************************************
Unid=1
!!! *** Width HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID, A,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1,0,0,unID, A,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, 0,unID, A,2 : unID=unID+1
!!! *** HEIGHT HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID, ZZYZX,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,-1,unID, ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX,unID, ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID, ZZYZX,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,0,-1,unID, ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,0,ZZYZX,unID, ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Depth HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID, B,1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1, 0,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B, 0,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID, B,1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B, 0,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,ZZYZX,unID, B,1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1, ZZYZX,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B, ZZYZX,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX,unID, B,1 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1, ZZYZX,unID, B,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B, ZZYZX,unID, B,2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A/2,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2,0,ZZYZX,unID : unID=unID+1
!!! *** Waste Container Height ADD 0, -WasteContOverhang, BoxThk HOTSPOT A/2,0,0,unID, WasteContHgt,1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2,0,-1,unID, WasteContHgt,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2,0,WasteContHgt,unID, WasteContHgt,2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
!!! ************************************************************* !!! *** 3D MODEL ************************************************
!!! *** Cabinet *************************************************
IF GLOB_CONTEXT=43 OR GLOB_CONTEXT=44 OR GLOB_CONTEXT=46 THEN !!! *** If the user want to substract the cabinet from the wall MATERIAL 5 PRISM_ 5,ZZYZX, 0,0,15, A,0,15, A,B,15, 0,B,15, 0,0,-1 ENDIF
ADD A/2,B,0
ROTx 90
MATERIAL CabinetMat !!! *** Box / Top, Bottom, Lateral Parts PRISM_ 10, B, -A*0.5, 0, 15, A*0.5, 0, 15, A*0.5, zzyzx, 15, -A*0.5, zzyzx, 15, -A*0.5, 0, -1, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, 10, A*0.5-BoxThk, BoxThk, 10, A*0.5-BoxThk, zzyzx-(BoxThk), 10, -A*0.5+BoxThk, zzyzx-(BoxThk), 10, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, -1
!!! *** Box /Rear Part PRISM_ 5, BoxThk, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, 12, A*0.5-(BoxThk), BoxThk, 12, A*0.5-(BoxThk), zzyzx-(BoxThk), 12, -A*0.5+BoxThk, zzyzx-(BoxThk), 12, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, 12
!!! *** Frame
MATERIAL FlangeMat ADDz B
PRISM_ 10,FrameThk, -A*0.5-FrameWidth, -FrameWidth, 15, A*0.5+FrameWidth, -FrameWidth, 15, A*0.5+FrameWidth, zzyzx+FrameWidth, 15, -A*0.5-FrameWidth, zzyzx+FrameWidth, 15, -A*0.5-FrameWidth, -FrameWidth, -1, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, 14, A*0.5-BoxThk, BoxThk, 14, A*0.5-BoxThk, zzyzx-BoxThk, 14, -A*0.5+BoxThk, zzyzx-BoxThk, 14, -A*0.5+BoxThk, BoxThk, -1
DEL 2
DEL 1
!!! *** Waste Container *****************************************
WasteContWidth= A- 2*(BoxThk)
ADD BoxThk, -WasteContDepth+B-BoxThk, BoxThk
MATERIAL WasteContMat
IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE THEN PRISM_ 10, WasteContHgt, 0, 0, 15, WasteContWidth, 0, 15, WasteContWidth, WasteContDepth, 15, 0, WasteContDepth, 15, 0, 0, -1, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, 14, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContThk, 14, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 14, WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 14, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, -1
PRISM_ 5, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, 12, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContThk, 12, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 12, WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 12, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, -1
ELSE
RR2=RR1-WasteContThk PRISM_ 22, WasteContHgt, 0, RR1, 79, RR1, RR1, 900, RR1,90, 4000, RR1, 0, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, 0, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, RR1, 900, RR1,90, 4000, WasteContWidth, RR1, 79, WasteContWidth, WasteContDepth, 15, 0, WasteContDepth, 15, 0, RR1, -1, WasteContThk, RR1, 79, RR1, RR1, 900, RR2,90, 4000, RR1, WasteContThk, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, WasteContThk, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, RR1, 900, RR2,90, 4000, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, RR1, 79, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 15, WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 15, WasteContThk, RR1, -1
PRISM_ 11, WasteContThk, WasteContThk, RR1, 79, RR1, RR1, 900, RR2,90, 4000, RR1, WasteContThk, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, WasteContThk, 79, WasteContWidth-RR1, RR1, 900, RR2,90, 4000, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, RR1, 79, WasteContWidth-WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 15, WasteContThk, WasteContDepth-WasteContThk, 15, WasteContThk, RR1, -1
ENDIF
DEL 1
Symbol.Script_2D:
unID=1
!!! *** Cabinet
HOTSPOT2 A/2 , 0, unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
ADD2 A,0 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1, unID, B, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
IF iSymbType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED THEN HOTSPOT2 -FrameWidth , 0, unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A+FrameWidth , 0, unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
!! *** Waste Container IF iSymbType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED THEN temp=BoxThk ELSE temp=0 ENDIF
ADD2 temp, 0 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, WasteContOverhang, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, 1, unID, WasteContOverhang, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -WasteContOverhang, unID, WasteContOverhang, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ADD2 A-(temp), 0 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, WasteContOverhang, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, 1, unID, WasteContOverhang, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -WasteContOverhang, unID, WasteContOverhang, 2 : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 !!! *** Cabinet *************************************************
ADD2 A/2,B
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
LINE_TYPE CabinetLineType ADD2 0,0 POLY2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, 0, 3, A*0.5, -B, 0, -A*0.5, -B, 3, -A*0.5, 0, 3
IF iSymbType = SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE THEN LINE2 -A*0.5, -B, A*0.5, -B DEL 1
ADD2 A*0.5, -B IF iSymbType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED THEN LINE_TYPE 1 POLY2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, 0, 3, FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, -FrameThk, 3, -A-FrameWidth, 0, 3 ENDIF DEL 1 DEL 1
!!! *** Waste Container *****************************************
IF iSymbType = SYMBTYPE_DETAILED THEN WasteContWidth= A- 2*(BoxThk) ADD2 BoxThk, -WasteContDepth+B-BoxThk LINE_TYPE 1 POLY2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, WasteContWidth, 0, 1, WasteContWidth, WasteContOverhang-FrameThk, 1, 0, WasteContOverhang-FrameThk, 1, 0, 0, 1
DEL 1
ELSE
WasteContWidth= A ADD2 0, -WasteContDepth+B-BoxThk LINE_TYPE 1 POLY2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, WasteContWidth, 0, 1, WasteContWidth, WasteContOverhang, 0, 0, WasteContOverhang, 1, 0, 0, 1
DEL 1
ENDIF
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iSymbType SYMBTYPE_DETAILED = 1 SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE = 2
dim stSymbType[2] stSymbType[1] = `Детальный` stSymbType[2] = `Простая`
! const values for parameter: iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED = 1 DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE = 2 DETLEVEL3D_OFF = 3
dim typRes[3] typRes[1] = `Детальный` typRes[2] = `Простая` typRes[3] = `Откл.`
FrameWidth = 0.02 FrameThk = 0.005 BoxThk = 0.004 WasteContThk = 0.006 RR1 = 0.04 ! radius of waste container edge

ui_pict 1, xPict, yPict, pictWidth, pictHeight,1 _yCurr = yPict - 22 ui_infield "B", x2, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Глубина Контейнера` ui_infield "A", x3, _yCurr, 90, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Ширина Контейнера`

_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_cont_pen" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_contourPen_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_fill_type" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_fillType_flat(1)"
_idx = _idx + 1 paramNameReprArray [_idx] = "gs_fill_pen" childFlagReprArray [_idx] = 1 iconNameReprArray [_idx] = "ui_list_fillPen_flat(1)"

Symbol.Script_VL:
! --- Bottom, Top Level Calculation --- ac_toplevel = ac_bottomlevel + ZZYZX parameters ac_toplevel = ac_toplevel
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, typRes[1], DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE, typRes[2], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, typRes[3]
VALUES{2} "iSymbType" SYMBTYPE_DETAILED, stSymbType[1], SYMBTYPE_SIMPLE, stSymbType[2]
VALUES "A" RANGE [(BoxThk+RR1)*2+0.01,) VALUES "B" RANGE [BoxThk+0.01,) VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [(BoxThk)*2+WasteContHgt+0.01,) VALUES "WasteContHgt" RANGE [WasteContThk+0.01,) VALUES "WasteContOverhang" RANGE [FrameThk,)
VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
PARAMETERS WasteContDepth=B-BoxThk+WasteContOverhang LOCK "WasteContDepth" HIDEPARAMETER "WasteContDepth"
